reviewText: Very good from Juanita as always
Juanita Bynum continues to teach THE WORD OF GOD!!!  This WORD helped me....it let's me know when I say I'm going to do something, I need to honor my word.

What an amazing and timeless message from a true Prophetess of God. The word of God came through with such utterance and fluidity, clearly evidencing the anointing that was working in God's servant. I am truly thankful to God for his hand upon Juanita Bynum's life and her surrender as a vessel for his service and ministry, especially in delivering this sobering, transforming, life changing word to God's people. The complete Camp Meeting service was not covered in this DVD, which was a bit disheartening, but I am glad for the recording nonetheless. Such a blessing!

I received my product before the date promised and it arrived in excellent condition. However I would suggest the Seller list the product description/format/type in larger print, and not fine print. As this was the case of my order, the fine print listed the product as a DVD, and I thought I was ordering a CD. I guess I will no better next time.
This is an excellent dvd to watch with the family.  It arrived packaged well and non-damaged.  I watch it over and over and each time I get something new from it.
I HEARD SNIPPET'S OF THIS MESSAGE ON YOUTUBE AND DECIDED TO BUY THE FULL MESSAGE ON AMAZON. I LOVE IT. IT'S A GREAT PREACHED MESSAGE.
Juanita Bynum truly allowed the Lord to use her in delivering this message.  She is to be commended on her obedience to His Word and her deliverance of His Word.

Another anointed message from Juanita Bynum.  This ain't for the "babies", it's for the ones ready to grow up and be accountable...surpassing just asking God for things, but really ready to sacrifice for the kingdom.
